data.description: Welcome to 620 Cherry St, nestled in the charming town of Anaconda, MT, where picturesque landscapes meet small-town warmth. This delightful 2-story house, boasting 4 bedrooms with the option of a 5th bedroom or office/craft room, is ideal for growing families, savvy investors, or those embarking on the journey of homeownership. The heart of the home is a dining room designed for memorable gatherings, while an upstairs bathroom, partially remodeled, is brimming with potential to become your personal oasis. The property also features a detached 2 car garage, complemented by a large shed complete with its own garage door—perfect for your vehicles, workshop projects, or storage needs. Imagine the life you can build within these walls, filled with laughter, dreams, and comfort. Don't miss the opportunity to plant your roots at 620 Cherry St, where your family's story can flourish. Discover how this home can be the canvas for your future.
